@startuml
title Diagrama de Secuencia - Crear Curso
actor "Administrador" as Admin
participant "Frontend (React)" as FE
participant "API (FastAPI)" as API
participant "CursoService" as Service
participant "CursoRepository" as Repo
database "Base de Datos" as DB
Admin -> FE: Clic en "Nuevo Curso"
activate FE
FE --> Admin: Mostrar Formulario
Admin -> FE: Ingresa nombre del curso y Guardar
FE -> API: POST /cursos (CursoCreate JSON)
activate API
API -> Service: crear_curso(curso_create)
activate Service
Service -> Repo: create(curso_model)
activate Repo
Repo -> DB: INSERT INTO cursos ...
activate DB
DB --> Repo: ID nuevo curso
deactivate DB
Repo --> Service: Curso (con ID)
deactivate Repo
Service --> API: CursoResponse
deactivate Service
API --> FE: 201 Created (Curso JSON)
deactivate API
FE -> FE: Actualizar Lista / Notificar Éxito
FE --> Admin: Mostrar "Curso creado correctamente"
deactivate FE
@enduml
